245
00:10:51,000 --> 00:10:53,000
He could be poisoned.

246
00:10:53,670 --> 00:10:56,200
I wonder if you recognize
these five divine treasures.

247
00:10:56,200 --> 00:10:58,390
These five are all
ancient divine treasures.

248
00:10:58,840 --> 00:11:00,080
I have heard of them,

249
00:11:00,790 --> 00:11:02,910
but I think no one's ever seen them.

250
00:11:03,320 --> 00:11:04,030
Mr. Bu.

251
00:11:04,270 --> 00:11:06,200
The Lingxi Pavilion has almost

252
00:11:06,200 --> 00:11:08,840
collected all the treasures
in the world.

253
00:11:08,910 --> 00:11:10,670
Except for these five divine treasures,

254
00:11:10,910 --> 00:11:12,910
I've yet to see them.

255
00:11:14,080 --> 00:11:15,790
Master Yu, don't be obsessed.

256
00:11:16,150 --> 00:11:17,910
Perhaps it's just a legend.

257
00:11:17,960 --> 00:11:19,320
Mr. Bu, let me tell you.

258
00:11:19,320 --> 00:11:20,840
Our Yu family for generations

259
00:11:20,840 --> 00:11:23,270
have devoted their lives
to finding these five divine treasures.

260
00:11:23,440 --> 00:11:25,320
When I was young, I believed

261
00:11:25,320 --> 00:11:27,200
that I could make it done.

262
00:11:28,240 --> 00:11:29,790
Sadly, so much time has passed.

263
00:11:29,790 --> 00:11:32,480
I haven't seen one yet.

264
00:11:32,670 --> 00:11:34,270
It might be as you said,

265
00:11:34,750 --> 00:11:36,600
just a legend.

266
00:11:40,960 --> 00:11:43,000
Yu Xinglan, where are you?

267
00:11:43,000 --> 00:11:44,360
Come out, Yu Xinglan.

268
00:11:45,630 --> 00:11:46,600
Yu Xinglan.

269
00:11:52,080 --> 00:11:53,840
Yu Xinglan, come out!

270
00:11:55,240 --> 00:11:56,270
Yu Xinglan.

271
00:11:56,750 --> 00:11:57,790
Mr. Gu.

272
00:11:58,000 --> 00:11:59,670
It's an honor to have you here.

273
00:12:00,240 --> 00:12:01,200
Our store

274
00:12:01,200 --> 00:12:02,390
