quite a few new items lately.

275
00:12:02,790 --> 00:12:05,150
All are rare treasures
from the Immortal Realm.

276
00:12:05,720 --> 00:12:08,960
Someone discerning like you,

277
00:12:09,080 --> 00:12:11,200
