have a fruitful return today.

278
00:12:12,270 --> 00:12:15,670
This Lingxi Pavilion indeed
has countless treasures.

279
00:12:16,480 --> 00:12:17,320
What's more important is

280
00:12:17,870 --> 00:12:19,440
having someone like you,

281
00:12:19,790 --> 00:12:21,120
